call them little penguins.

36:38.334 --> 36:42.209
But fairy penguins
is the name they prefer.

36:42.376 --> 36:45.042
And they're small and quick.

36:45.209 --> 36:47.376
Here one minute, gone the next.

36:47.542 --> 36:49.459
And every time you see them,

36:49.626 --> 36:52.126
